events.name: Node js Workshop

venue.name: Higher Institute of Applied Science and Technology of Sousse

events.description:
This is an intensive hands-on workshop to fast track full-fledged enterprise application development on the NodeJS platform. The first of a 2 part series on NodeJS, focusing on establishing a strong foundation in server side Javascript.

You’ll walk away from this 2-day course confident in your ability to:

Build applications using one of the most widely used Javascript server side engines
Build middleware using the Express Framework
Use Javascript as a full-stack programming language

events.name: IWD'2020
events.description:
For all the makers, the fighters, the strong women out there who can move mountains and build cities with their bare hands with their voices and even their silence, women making change, creating history and challenging them selves because they can 💪💪this is your call🤩
The International Women's Day is the day that will make us remember and appreciate the impact that women have been making in the tech industry and beyond.
IWD will be organized by Women Techmakers Sousse on sunday April 19th, 2020.
We are honored to host this spectacular women reunion .
So let's make IWD our day to spread joy and influence all the young ladies out there to show them that they matter that they are strong, powerful, loved and #Remarkable .
We will be so glad to have you with us students, professionals and passionate women.
We planned games, workshops, conferences and a competition 💥🔥🔥 along with animation and motivation 🤗.
There will be a balanced combination between fun and technology.
